{"id": 7227, "title": "Ticket #7227: Introduce JobSets into the schedd", "description": "<blockquote>\nIntroduce sets of jobs as a first-class citizen into the schedd.\n\n<p>Design document is at\n<a class=\"external\" href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1JtXS-7rTFlbQwzqEewXwFl_n6nkDOXGO\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1JtXS-7rTFlbQwzqEewXwFl_n6nkDOXGO</a>\n\n</p><p>Documenting <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=JobSets\" title=\"Job Sets\">JobSets</a></span> will happen in a future ticket after we think more about the user interface for this functionality.\n\n</p><p>The default value for config knob <code>USE_JOBSETS</code> will be False for now, meaning this functionality is disabled.  A future ticket will enable it to True by default.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"new\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=7388\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7388'); return false;\" title=\"Initial pass at associating input files with a JobSet\">#7388</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\nInitial pass at associating input files with a <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=JobSet\" title=\"Job Set\">JobSet</a></span></td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">\n<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=7751\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7751'); return false;\" title=\"JobSets attribute NextJobSetNum is confusing behavior\">#7751</a></span></td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"center\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon ptr1\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\">\n<span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=JobSets\" title=\"Job Sets\">JobSets</a></span> attribute <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=NextJobSetNum\" title=\"Next Job Set Num\">NextJobSetNum</a></span> is confusing behavior</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Nov-13 17:31</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=58465\">[58465]</a></span>: Remember if a job is not in any set to avoid ad lookups. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=7227\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7227'); return false;\" title=\"Introduce JobSets into the schedd\">#7227</a></span> Now a <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=JobQueueJob\" title=\"Job Queue Job\">JobQueueJob</a></span> set_id member is 0 if we do not yet know the set id, and -1 if we know the job is not a member of a set.  (By Todd Tannenbaum )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Nov-13 17:28</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=58464\">[58464]</a></span>: Fix bugs when switching USE_JOBSETS knob from false to true. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=7227\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7227'); return false;\" title=\"Introduce JobSets into the schedd\">#7227</a></span>  (By Todd Tannenbaum )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Nov-13 17:24</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=58463\">[58463]</a></span>: Fix bug restoring next <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=JobSet\" title=\"Job Set\">JobSet</a></span> ID to use on schedd startup. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=7227\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7227'); return false;\" title=\"Introduce JobSets into the schedd\">#7227</a></span>  (By Todd Tannenbaum )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Nov-13 13:43</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=58460\">[58460]</a></span>: Initial implementation for <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=JobSets\" title=\"Job Sets\">JobSets</a></span> in the schedd. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=7227\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7227'); return false;\" title=\"Introduce JobSets into the schedd\">#7227</a></span>  (By Todd Tannenbaum )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "enhance", "last_change": "2020-Jul-24 08:34", "status": "resolved", "created": "2019-Aug-30 13:26", "fixed_version": "2019-Aug-30 13:26", "broken_version": "", "priority": "3", "subsystem": "DaemonsSubmitNode", "assigned_to": "tannenba", "derived_from": "", "creator": "tannenba", "rust": "", "customer_group": "chtc", "visibility": "public", "notify": "", "due_date": ""}